user.text: What is the Web extension for federal government websites and how do we ensure the site is secure?

agent.speaker: agent
agent.text: The web extension for federal government websites often ends in .gov or .mil. To ensure the site is secure, look for the "https://" in the website's URL. This indicates that you are connected to the official website and any information you provide will be encrypted and transmitted securely.
